snippet.title: DeathSprint 66 - Official Release Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the Death Sprint 66 release date trailer. DeathSprint 66 is an action hardcore arcade on-foot racing game developed by Sumo Digital. Players will take off on foot and evade deadly obstacles to push their limits and reign victorious. Use brutal abilities and achieve velocities unlike any other. DeathSprint 66 is launching on September 12 for PC (Steam).

#DeathSprint66 #Gaming #Games
